\begin{align*}
\cos{\theta} &= \frac{1}{2} \\
\theta &= \cos^{-1}\left(\frac{1}{2}\right) \\
\theta &= 60^{\circ}
\end{align*}
Thus, the angle between the unit vectors $\mathbf{a}$ and $\mathbf{b}$ is $\boxed{60^{\circ}}$.

